text: Emmering is a community in the Upper Bavarian district of Ebersberg. It is a member of the administrative community (Verwaltungsgemeinschaft) of Aßling. ==Geography== Emmering is in the Munich region. It includes one traditional rural land unit – Gemarkung in German – also called Emmering. ==References== Category:Ebersberg (district)
title: Emmering, Ebersberg
